sequenceDiagram
  participant B as CP Master BDMA
  participant TOP as TOP/HCQD regs
  participant U as CP User sf/cmd_entry
  participant CPE as CPE regs

  B->>TOP: write STOP_HCQDID bit
  TOP-->>U: stop interrupt / stopped bitmap
  U->>U: drop IB resident packets
  U->>CPE: set CPE_FW_HCQD_STOPPED bit
  B->>TOP: poll HCQD_STATUS stop complete
  B->>CPE: poll CPE_FW_HCQD_STOPPED bit
  B->>TOP: set RELEASE_HCQDID bit
  B->>TOP: wait HCQD idle
  B->>TOP: clear RELEASE_HCQDID bit
  B->>CPE: clear CPE_FW_HCQD_STOPPED bit
  B->>TOP: clear STOP_HCQDID
